parameters.name: application
parameters.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the robot application.

nested_items.name: arn
nested_items.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the robot application.

nested_items.name: name
nested_items.description: The name of the robot application.

nested_items.name: version
nested_items.description: The version of the robot application.

nested_items.name: sources
nested_items.description: The sources of the robot application.

nested_items.name: etag
nested_items.description: A hash of the object specified by s3Bucket and s3Key.

nested_items.name: architecture
nested_items.description: The taget processor architecture for the application.

nested_items.name: robotSoftwareSuite
nested_items.description: The robot software suite used by the robot application.

nested_items.name: name
nested_items.description: The name of the robot software suite. General is the only supported value.

nested_items.name: version
nested_items.description: The version of the robot software suite. Not applicable for General software suite.

nested_items.name: revisionId
nested_items.description: The revision id of the robot application.

nested_items.name: lastUpdatedAt
nested_items.description: The time, in milliseconds since the epoch, when the robot application was last updated.

nested_items.name: environment
nested_items.description: The object that contains the Docker image URI used to create the robot application.

nested_items.name: uri
nested_items.description: The Docker image URI for either your robot or simulation applications.

nested_items.name: imageDigest
nested_items.description: A SHA256 identifier for the Docker image that you use for your robot application.
